OL,3,CNewcastle United sign Sean Steur as
OL,4,Cfuture of Bruno Guimaraes becomes
OL,5,Cunclear
OL,7,FNewcastle United have confirmed they
OL,8,Fhave completed the signing of Ajax
OL,9,Fmidfielder Sean Steur.
OL,11,FThe 18-year-old has signed a five-year
OL,12,Fdeal at St James' Park and will wear
OL,13,Fthe number 14 shirt.
OL,15,FHe is the Magpies' third signing of
OL,16,Fthe summer following the arrival of
OL,17,FFrench goalkeeper Ewen Jaouen and
OL,18,FIvorian winger Bazoumana Toure.
OL,26,@lD@WtpzD@^rr
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
