FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784182683
OL,3,CNewcastle United sign Sean Steur as
OL,4,Cfuture of Bruno Guimaraes becomes
OL,5,Cunclear
OL,7,F"It's an incredible feeling to be
OL,8,Fhere," Steur said. "It's a giant club
OL,9,Fin the Premier League and it was
OL,10,Falways my dream to play in the best
OL,11,Fleague in the world, so this is really
OL,12,Fexciting.
OL,14,F"I was at home at Ajax ` I joined when
OL,15,FI was seven and I leave with only good
OL,16,Fmemories, but when a club like
OL,17,FNewcastle comes for you, it's really
OL,18,Fhard to say no. The last few days have
OL,19,Fgone fast and I'm very happy to join."
OL,26,@lD@WtpoD@AOUvD@AOU
