OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784182683
OL,3,CNewcastle United sign Sean Steur as
OL,4,Cfuture of Bruno Guimaraes becomes
OL,5,Cunclear
OL,7,FNewcastle Head Coach Eddie Howe,
OL,8,Fadded: "We're delighted to welcome
OL,9,FSean to Newcastle United ` he's a top
OL,10,Fyoung prospect that has already tasted
OL,11,FChampions League and top-flight Dutch
OL,12,Ffootball.
OL,14,F"We see real potential in Sean and
OL,15,Fbelieve he has the characteristics to
OL,16,Fbecome a valuable player for us for
OL,17,Fyears to come. That's something we're
OL,18,Freally excited by and look forward to
OL,19,Fworking with him and helping him
OL,20,Fachieve his ambitions.
OL,26,@lD@WtppD@HOUvD@AOU
