PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784182683
OL,3,CNewcastle United sign Sean Steur as
OL,4,Cfuture of Bruno Guimaraes becomes
OL,5,Cunclear
OL,7,F"Sean is an exciting addition to our
OL,8,Fsquad. He's had an excellent
OL,9,Fupbringing at Ajax, who have an
OL,10,Foutstanding track record of producing
OL,11,Fyoung players."
OL,13,FSteur's arrival coincides with
OL,14,Funcertainty surrounding the future of
OL,15,FNewcastle's captain Bruno Guimaraes.
OL,26,@lD@WtpoD@AOUwD@atp
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
