PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784182683
OL,3,CNewcastle United sign Sean Steur as
OL,4,Cfuture of Bruno Guimaraes becomes
OL,5,Cunclear
OL,7,FThe 28-year-old is believed to have
OL,8,Ftold club officials that he would like
OL,9,Fto leave Tyneside this summer, with
OL,10,FPremier League champions Arsenal
OL,11,Fbelieved to be his preferred
OL,12,Fdestination.
OL,14,FNewcastle are said to have no desire
OL,15,Fto sell and have received no approach
OL,16,Ffrom Arsenal.
OL,18,FAnthony Gordon and Sandro Tonali have
OL,19,Falready left the club this summer for
OL,20,Fa combined total of around #170m.
OL,26,@lD@Wtp
